title: デビュー戦の後に・まず目指すは！

text_block_list.text: Matikanetannhauser finished her debut race with a smile, saying 'Fun!' without being intimidated by the intensity of the Twinkle Series.
The audience, seeing Matikanetannhauser's race was on another level, began dreaming of a showdown with the large-scale newcomer Mihono Bourbon, who debuted the other day.
After returning home, she set her goal in the Classic Year as 'Achieving the Classic Triple Crown'—
As a first step up, she decided to aim for 'Top 5 in a G1 race'!
